<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-10-05T14:44:15-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-10-05T14:44:15-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T14:44:15-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的电子书阅读器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;蓝色背景下空中漂浮的各种物体&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ahl9GA-W3_l8GrBRn3vh1DQwhUU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72396035/236754_Best_ebook_readers_for_2023_WJoel.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Will Joel / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从在浴缸里读书到在浴缸里乱写乱画从深入亚马逊生态系统到彻底避开它，每个人都有一款电子阅读器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-读者&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T14:36:47-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T14:36:47-04:00</updated><title>三星正在向三星钱包添加对移动驾驶执照的支持</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hcac_IA2KDVO9_3076TFtuwSQW4=/100x0:1180x720/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72725011 /samsung_wallet_drivers_licenses.0.png&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;5wlIKr&quot;>;三星将允许亚利桑那州和爱荷华州的客户从本月晚些时候开始将驾驶​​执照添加到三星电子钱包，三星的 Sally Hyesoon Jeong 在台上表示。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/live/ax71_UYDk3Y?feature=shared&amp;amp;t=5504&quot;>;周四举行的 2023 年三星开发者大会&lt;/a>;。目前尚不清楚何时会支持更多州，但 Jeong 确实表示，从明年开始，三星客户还将“能够使用三星钱包在线验证您的驾驶执照。”&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float -left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;BoXu2G&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;三星钱包又回来了，可以整理您的 ID、密钥和加密货币&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/6/16/23169586/samsung-wallet-pay-pass-id-keys-boarding -pass&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;3ITjOZ&quot;>;这项新功能使三星与苹果和谷歌的关系更加紧密，这两家公司也都提供了节省驾驶员时间的功能移动钱包中来自选定州的许可证。亚利桑那州成为第一个正式支持 Apple 解决方案的州 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/3/23/22992745/apple-wallet-license-arizona-colorado-hawaii-real-id&quot;>; 2022 年 3 月&lt;/a>;，以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5mac.com/2023/09/04/apple-wallet-digital-ids-support-states/#:~:text=As%20it% 20stands%20today%2C%20only，详细信息%20of%20their%20implementations%20here&quot;>;由 &lt;em>;9to5Mac&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;、科罗拉多州、马里兰州和...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905072/samsung-wallet-mobile-drivers-licenses&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905072/samsung-wallet-mobile-drivers-licenses" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23905072/samsung-wallet-mobile-drivers-licenses</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T13:30:40-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T13:30:40-04:00</updated><title>这是焕然一新的 Steam Deck 即将到来的第一个证据</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;带有双摇杆和触摸板的黑色游戏手持设备位于橙色和白色背景上的开放式灰色拉链织物盒中&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xytSTgiGtJANJnMj1RloVVxf_Wo =/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72724731/vpavic_220210_5030_0096.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Steam Deck，位于附带的手提箱中。&lt;/ EM>; |摄影：Vjeran Pavic / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ulOxgg&quot;>;我想我们不会只是得到一个新的 Steam Deck &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023 /9/21/23884863/valve-steam-deck-2-refresh-upgrade-cpu-2025&quot;>;因为 Valve 还没有准备好升级其性能&lt;/a>;？再想一想：根据机构文件显示，Valve 已经于 8 月 13 日通过了 FCC 的认证程序，让新的 Steam Deck 生效。 &lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：FCC&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：FCC&lt;/cite>; &lt;/图>; &lt;p id=&quot;YGVFVK&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/7/23863862/valve-galileo-sephiroth-1030-south-korea-radio-certification&quot;>;通过韩国国家无线电研究机构的神秘“Valve 1030”&lt;/a>;现已被明确确定为 Steam Deck，这是我们第一个证明该硬件可能足够接近发布以证明向监管机构展示它的合理性。 p>; &lt;p id=&quot;MoJH7M&quot;>;为什么我们现在才知道这个？因为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/7/23863862/valve-galileo-sephiroth-1030-south-korea-radio-certification#:~:text=Valve%20management%20to %20get%20the%20Steam%20Deck%20past%20the%20FCC%20without%20being%20spotted%20early%2C%20by%20having%20its%20Wi%2DFi%20/%20Bluetooth%20vendor%20Realtek%20re%2Dcertify%20the% 20wireless%20module%20rather%20than%20certifying%20the%20Steam%20Deck%20itself。&quot;>;就像最初的 Steam Deck&lt;/a>; 一样，Valve 使用其 Wi-Fi 和蓝牙芯片供应商来偷偷通过。 Valve 侦探 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SadlyItsBradley/status/1709644205084021226&quot;>;Brad Lynch 和 @TVKilledMi...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T13:00:11-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T13:00:11-04:00</updated><title>三星刚刚将其条形音箱变成了 SmartThings 中心</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;条形音箱和电视。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gUOwf5tIH-xWAmi5DZ4hN7jBrVg=/56x0:653x398/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72724615/2023_Soundbar_HW_Q900C_KV_0 1_PC.5.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;三星最新的条形音箱 HW-Q900C 现在能够成为 SmartThings 中心&lt;/em>; |图片：三星&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;qBSGTA&quot;>;在今天的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.samsungdeveloperconference.com/&quot;>;年度开发者大会&lt;/a>;上，三星再次将其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.smartthings.com/&quot;>;SmartThings 智能家居平台&lt;/a>;放在首位，宣布其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://news.samsung.com/us /samsung-introduces-new-premium-soundbar-lineup-2023/&quot;>;最新的条形音箱 HW-Q900C&lt;/a>; 现在能够成为 SmartThings 中心，并支持 Zigbee，&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/23165855/thread-smart-home-protocol-matter-apple-google-interview&quot;>;主题&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 22787729/matter-smart-home-standard-apple-amazon-google&quot;>;事情&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eJ0DMZ&quot;>;这家电子巨头在过去几年中一直在积极推动 SmartThings，致力于连接来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ 的所有电器、电视、智能手机和小工具。 /www.theverge.com/2023/8/29/23850250/samsung-lg-app-home-connectivity-alliance-appliances-ifa&quot;>;其他制造商&lt;/a>;一起构建基于物联网的统一智能家居生态系统。在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.smartthings.com/hub-everywhere&quot;>;Hub Everywhere 计划&lt;/a>;中添加条形音箱是该公司将智能家居中心置于无处不在的追求的延续，目标是让人们更轻松地开始使用联网家庭。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;9e2l14&quot;>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904754/samsung-sdc23-soundbar-smartthings-smart-home-hub&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904754/samsung-sdc23-soundbar-smartthings-smart-home-hub" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904754/samsung-sdc23-soundbar-smartthings-smart-home-hub</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T12:46:42-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T12:46:42-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 活动 The Verge 指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;亚马逊包裹堆叠的彩色动画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TgkdLDBWr1XQyFpzJiwmK58WVzs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72721616/236765_Prime_Big_Deal_Day